PMID: 23587118. 

See Table 4"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0001913> "computation run time is a time measurement datum which corresponds the time expressed in second, minute, hour necessary for a computer program to complete a process execution, for example genome assembly. It is an important metrics as it indicates the resource occupancy and computer program efficiency."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000118> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0001913> "computation run time datum"@en)
